Uses of Class
gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.discoveryengine.MudrodAbstract

  • Packages that use MudrodAbstract 
    Package Description
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.discoveryengine
    This package includes abstract classes of MUDROD, discovery step, and engine.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.integration
    This package includes integration method of web log, ontology, and metdata mining results.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.metadata.pre
    This package includes metadata pre-processing functions.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.metadata.process
    This package includes metadata processing classes.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.ontology.pre
    This package includes ontology pre-processing classes.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.ontology.process
    This package includes ontology processing classes.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.recommendation.pre
    This package includes the preprocessing required by recommendation module.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.recommendation.process
    This package includes the processing required by recommendation module.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.recommendation.structure
    This package includes the data structure required by recommendation module.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.semantics
    This package includes SVD transformation function, methods of calculating similarity from CSV, and saving triples into Elasticsearch
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.ssearch
    This package includes classes for semantic search, such as click stream importer, query dispatcher, semantic searcher, and ranker (ranksvm, ordinal/linear regression)
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.ssearch.ranking
    This package includes classes for importing training data, ML models, generating input data for RankSVM, and evaluating ranking results
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.utils
    This package includes utilities classes for calculating similarity and parsing HTTP request
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.weblog.pre
    This package includes Preprocessing for all functionality required by the WeblogDiscoveryEngine
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.weblog.process
    This package includes web log processing classes.
    gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.weblog.structure
    This package includes data structure needed for web log analysis
